OL,3,CNurse in transgender colleague
OL,4,Ctribunal case feared 'bigot' label
OL,6,FA nurse taking her hospital trust to
OL,7,Fan employment tribunal over its policy
OL,8,Fof allowing a transgender colleague to
OL,9,Fuse the female changing-rooms said she
OL,10,Fwas initially wary of raising concerns
OL,11,Fas she feared being labelled a bigot.
OL,13,FTracey Hooper is one of eight nurses
OL,14,Fbringing a claim against County Durham
OL,15,Fand Darlington NHS Foundation Trust
OL,16,Fafter Rose Henderson, who was born
OL,17,Fmale but who identifies as a woman,
OL,18,Fwas allowed to use the women's
OL,19,Fchanging facilities at Darlington
OL,20,FMemorial Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
