OL,6,FIn her witness statement, Ms Hooper
OL,7,Fsaid she first became aware of Rose
OL,8,FHenderson using the female changing
OL,9,Frooms in the summer of 2023.
OL,11,FShe said: "I could not believe it. He
OL,12,Fwas dressed in a masculine way: he was
OL,13,Fwearing a baggy black t-shirt with a
OL,14,Flarge rock or gothic image on the
OL,15,Ffront, baggy jeans and well-used dark
OL,16,Ftrainers.
OL,18,F"He had long straggly hair. He wore no
OL,19,Fmake-up or jewellery."
