OL,6,F"At that point, I had also not heard
OL,7,Fanyone else say anything about it.
OL,9,F"So, I thought that everyone else was
OL,10,FOK with the situation and maybe I was
OL,11,Fthe only one to have an issue with it.
OL,12,FTherefore, I kept quiet about my
OL,13,Fconcerns."
OL,15,FMs Hooper said that changed when she
OL,16,Fspoke to other colleagues and some
OL,17,Freferred to Rose Henderson's
OL,18,F"inappropriate behaviour" in the
OL,19,Fchanging room.
