OL,6,FThe claimant said senior colleagues
OL,7,Fhad a meeting following complaints
OL,8,Ffrom staff and the response was "we
OL,9,Fhad to accept the situation due to the
OL,10,Finclusiveness of the NHS, despite the
OL,11,Ffact that a number of departments had
OL,12,Fraised the same issue".
OL,14,FMs Hooper said after the trust did not
OL,15,Fact on their concerns, they began the
OL,16,Flegal proceedings and gave media
OL,17,Finterviews following that decision.
OL,26,@pD@aOUtD@VO]
