OL,6,FShe said: "We felt the public needed
OL,7,Fto be aware of the situation we were
OL,8,Ffacing, as the trust was refusing to
OL,9,Fprotect our rights, and we believed
OL,10,Fsimilar problems might also be
OL,11,Fhappening up and down the country.
OL,13,F"I felt people needed to know this was
OL,14,Fhappening because this was unlawful
OL,15,Fand simply not right. We took legal
OL,16,Fadvice before going to the media to
OL,17,Fmake sure we did nothing illegal or
OL,18,Fimproper.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@AOU
