OL,6,F"We were hoping for some public
OL,7,Fsupport, but we could not have
OL,8,Fforeseen the amount of support we have
OL,9,Freceived in the past year.
OL,11,F"I went to the postroom to pick up the
OL,12,Fletters and cards that were sent to us
OL,13,Fafter the first media publication,
OL,14,Fthere must have been over 30 letters
OL,15,Fand cards that time. It was
OL,16,Fheartwarming to receive those
OL,17,Fencouraging messages."
