OL,11,FMs Hooper said in July 2024 the trust
OL,12,Fmade a manager's old office ` the size
OL,13,Fof a small box bedroom ` into an
OL,14,Falternative changing room but she said
OL,15,Fit was unsuitable as it opened
OL,16,Fdirectly onto a corridor.
