OL,6,FShe said: "Although some of us,
OL,7,Fincluding me, chose to use this room
OL,8,Frather than risk stripping off in
OL,9,Ffront of RH, we felt humiliated,
OL,10,Fostracised and very much let down by
OL,11,Four employer, who should have been
OL,12,Fensuring all staff were comfortable
OL,13,Fand safe at work, and claims to
OL,14,Fchampion respect and dignity for all."
OL,16,FThey are bringing a claim for sexual
OL,17,Fharassment, discrimination,
OL,18,Fvictimisation and breaches of the
OL,19,Fright to a private life, under article
OL,20,Feight of the European Convention on
OL,21,FHuman Rights.
