OL,6,FIn their particulars of claim
OL,7,Fdocument, the nurses say the health
OL,8,Ftrust "permits any member of staff
OL,9,F(regardless of sex and regardless of
OL,10,Fgender reassignment) to choose their
OL,11,F'gender identity' and to access a
OL,12,Fsingle-sex changing room on that
OL,13,Fbasis".
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the health trust
OL,16,Fsaid: "County Durham and Darlington
OL,17,FNHS Foundation Trust is committed to
OL,18,Fproviding safe, respectful and
OL,19,Finclusive care for patients and
OL,20,Fworking environment for all colleagues.
